{
  "stem": "3771.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I begged him, 'Don't switch your mind in the camp.' In the barracks, the following day, they just took you out and automatically you went to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was, every day, [INAUDIBLE] couldn't work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I begged him he should go work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[CRYING] He couldn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[SOBBING] And I came at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Here, I had friends I'd-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was actually the last link of my family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I holded-- I holded onto him so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[SOBBING] Half the time I used to take from my little piece of bread, and I will try to share it with him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He was young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was much younger than I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He must have been about 14 years, maybe. 14, 15 years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Such a beautiful-- he used to encourage me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he stayed in, and that was the end of him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I didn't see him anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Actually, I had some friends where I was want to commit suicide on myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I had there a-- a good friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I think-- the only thing what I remember he was from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He went from Pressburg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He was a professor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he was next to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We were next to the-- where we slept, or next to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he saw that I was losing it my mind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I'm going down and down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And he had a terrible inspiration on me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He said to me, 'That's what the Germans want.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "All of the families here are gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "You have to fight him to survive for your family alone.' And he-- day in and day out-- he had tremendous impact on me.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
